<Layout title="Gerrard Group Inc"
    description="Professional Industrial Auctions, Liquidations, Appraisals, Consulting Services and Used Machinery Sales. Experienced industrial asset and disposition experts in used CNC,vfabricating machinery & equipment, rubber & plastics, machine tools, coil processing, stamping presses and many others. Aerospace, mining, foundry, biotech, automotive, maerial handling, pharmaceuticals and more." 
    title2="Gerrard Group Inc" 
    url="https://www.gerrardgroupinc.com" 
    name="Gerrard Group Inc" 
    url2="https://www.gerrardgroupinc.com" 
    title3="Gerrard Group Inc" 
    url3="https://www.gerrardgroupinc.com"
    canon="https://www.gerrardgroupinc.com">
	<header class="welcome">
        <div>
            <h1 class="welcome-text"><strong><span class="intro"></span></strong><span class="cursor">&nbsp;</span></h1>
            <h1 class="moto-text"><strong><span class="moto"></span></strong><span class="cursor2">&nbsp;</span></h1>
        </div>
        <picture>
            <source media="(max-width:40rem)" srcset="../images/gerrard_montage_3_copy.jpg">
            <img class="banner" src="../images/gerrard_montage_3_copy2.jpg" alt="machines in a warehouse">
        </picture>
    </header>
    <main class="body-wrapper">
        <div class="container">
            <img class="img-workers" loading="lazy" src="../images/Factory+People+2.jpg" alt="people in a factory">
            <article class="comp-info">
                <h2><strong>About Gerrard Group / Gerrard Machinery Company</strong></h2>
                <p><strong>Gerrard Group / Gerrard Machinery Company</strong> specializes in Auctions and 
                    Liquidations for a wide variety of Machinery, Equipment and other Assets.
                    Our used machinery division, <strong>Gerrard Machinery Company, LLC</strong>, buys and 
                    sells industrial machinery and equipment as a regular course of business. 
                    This diversity gives us a broader understanding of both the retail and 
                    wholesale markets which puts our clients at a huge advantage. This, along 
                    with our strategic partners around the country and abroad, our group is 
                    able to service a wide variety of business sectors.</p>

                <p>In addition to Auctions and Liquidations, we provide Appraisal and 
                    Consulting Services to help determine <strong>highest possible returns</strong> of Company 
                    Assets. We are not a “High Volume” or “Cookie Cutter” company, we believe 
                    every project comes with its own needs and expectations. Our team has the 
                    knowledge, dedication and understanding you need.</p>

                <p>Whether it’s a single piece of equipment, plant relocation, multiple 
                    facilities, or demolition projects, we are your trusted source. Talk to 
                    one of our team members to discuss how we can help.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
            <article class="comp-special">
                <h2><strong>Gerrard Group / Gerrard Machinery Company Specializes In...</strong></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Auctions</li>
                    <li>Liquidation</li>
                    <li>Appraisals</li>
                    <li>Retail Used Machinery Sales</li>
                    <li>Machinery & Equipment Buy and Sell Programs</li>
                    <li>Demolition & Remediation Projects</li>
                    <li>Consulting</li>
                </ul>
            </article>
            <article class="industries">
                <h2><strong>Industries</strong></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fabricating, Metal, Rubber & Plastics Equip.</li>
                    <li>CNC & Robotics</li>
                    <li>Tooling & Support Equip.</li>
                    <li>Construction & Mining</li>
                    <li>Yellow Iron</li>
                    <li>Oil & Gas</li>
                    <li>Transportation</li>
                    <li>Aerospace</li>
                    <li>Energy Sector</li>
                    <li>Warehouse & Support</li>
                    <li>Food & Beverage</li>
                    <li>Pulp & Packaging</li>
                    <li>High-Tech & Biotech</li>
                    <li>Medical, Dental & Pharmaceutical</li>
                    <li>Raw, WIP & Finished Inventories<br> (used for, or made from
                    mfg. equipment)</li>
                </ul>
            </article>
        </div>
        <section class="locations">
            <h3><strong>Offices Located In:</strong></h3>
            <ul>
                <li>St. Louis, MO</li>
                <li>Chicago, IL</li>
                <li>Spokane, WA</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>

